Name: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' occurring after 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of process variants that include 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' relative to the total number of variants
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases

Name: Number of times 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' appears in cases that eventually reach 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' after a revision cycle
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' that is directly preceded by 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Frequency of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' compared to the frequency of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Percentage of cases containing 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' that eventually lead to 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Number of process variants where 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' occurs within three activities after 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' occurrences that are part of accepted manuscript trajectories (i.e., followed by final 'Manuscript Export Succeeded')
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Frequency of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' in relation to 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of all 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' events that are followed by 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of times 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' appears in variants that originated from a 'SW-EIC Accept' decision
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Ratio of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' occurrences to total number of 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' events
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Percentage of process instances where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' is observed and later followed by 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' grouped by case identifier to identify repeated occurrences per manuscript
Metric: Frequency of activity '{}' grouped by the last value of code
